column26: Get Johnny Depp back into Pirates 6
column33: Get Johnny Depp back into Pirates 6
column34:
Hello everyone! 

We are all fans of Johnny Depp, and even more so admire his role as Captain Jack Sparrow in Pirates of the Caribbean. Now, as some of you may know, Mr. Depp was fired by Disney to play in Pirates 6 due to the domestic abuse allegations set by Amber Heard. These allegations forced Disney to fire Mr. Depp from playing future roles in movies or in the Pirates of the Caribbean franchise. 


I created this petition because I do not believe that Mr. Depp did any wrong doing. I believe he is innocent and it just shows how allegations can ruin a persons career. So in order to prove to Disney that he belongs in Pirates 6, sign this petition and show your support for Mr. Depp. We all know that Pirates of the Caribbean could never be Pirates of the Caribbean without Captain Jack Sparrow! (And of course, sign this to get him future roles with Disney if the opportunity is ever given). Let’s make Disney look bad for making the decision to fire him and give him a second chance!
